Functionnal Requirements:
 1. Users can login and register into the system.
 2. Users are required to login using their username, and password.
 3. Users can update their profile information.
 4. Users have different access based on their role (admin, user).
 5. Users can create quizes and invite other users.
 6. Quizes have varaities of questions. text, MCQ, or TF. Quiz have certain allowed time.
 7. Quizes' questions can be left blank or answered. Based on the instructor choice.
 9. Users can search for quizes using quiz id.
10. Users can join a quiz N times. N is an integer that is set creator users.
11. Users can't join quiz with expired time.
12. System can, optionally, calculate users grades automatically.
13. System can allow users to view the model answer for a quiz after the quiz is finished.
14. System allows users to give feedback for a question in a quiz.

Other Functionnal Requirements:
 1. System shall automatically follow user default theme (dark/light mode).
 2. System shall be responsive to the change of canvas size.
 3. System shall be desgined for both mobile and desktop browsers.
 4. System shall follow a clean design with unified fonts, colors, and icons.
